n<br />\n茂木敏充說，期望協議在明年一月正式生效。<br />\n（香港電台）<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549095-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549095-20200911.htm&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=583f401c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549095-20200911.htm&h=dde18488\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549095-20200911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"896a2848f12ae0399f9b04a23d8309a22a27577c","tid":2198322,"uid":296410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T10:50:46.000Z","msg":"世柒有講，佢話英國借香港入CPTPP"}]}